// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1513 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: eb6f3131-88ca-5009-ac6c-beb42c5b462e

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
